data.description: Custom built home in the Tuluso-Midway school district. Lots of upgrades and special features. One of the largest lots in the neighborhood. Gated dog run, above ground pool, close to T-M High School. Four full bedrooms, two and a half baths. Dining area could be used as an office. Patio has custom built in TV, which will convey. Built in shelving in garage. Too many extras to list!! Schedule your showing today!
